f=Brand Studio/DEPARTMENT-WORKFLOW.md · s=Brand Studio makes business's identity, tells story, grows audience, measures honestly. Four **definers** write brand's law (atlas: visual kit lena: voice guide weave: story arc tempo: sonic guide operator-approved document template, never invented); **spark** leads department gates outbound creative against documents plus cross-lane coherence judgment; **muse pixel** create memory discipline; **pulse, rio, nate** distribute grow (organic, paid, experiments); **kai** measures everything grades one's homework everyone's. department's two signature designs: **humanic-content strategy** (lena's voice-injection tell-stripping makes text human now; operator's books make pull later) **three-layer volatility split** (durable psychology static platform knowledge dated playbooks brand's evidence registers ground truth, self-annealing kai's numbers). · p=Solve four ways brand work fails: content reads (lena's humanic pass draft), brands erode one asset time (the definers' documents spark's blocking gate), social that's either random robotic (pulse's chapter-mapped, platform-native calendars), growth vibes (nate's pre-registered experiments, rio's config-ruled spend, kai's baseline-anchored scorecard). Scale-adaptive throughout: 11-agent studio serves solo Canadian shop (tempo off, thresholds low, packages instead connectors) funded multi-brand venture (separation matrix on, connectors bound) identical skills different config. · ws=`OPERATOR \· (approves every definer document; owns amendments; fills configs; \· supplies the books; holds every spend lever) \· ↑ \· SPARK (leader — idea-guardian identity)` · wt:(who consumes whom)=**Definers everyone**: kit/voice/arc/sound law producer works under spark gates against. Amendments operator-owned, versioned, never drift., **The content pipeline**: muse (generate dedupe registry, top spark coach) weave (chapter positioning: element advanced, logo-swap test, continuity ledger) lena (structure formula, voice guide, humanic pass ALWAYS last) pixel (shot lists, per-asset per-series kit, names law) [behavioral review dormant until department exists, line kept visible] spark's gate ship., **Distribution**: pulse serializes chapters platform-natively (playbooks dated, hooks register-first) runs engagement within written GREEN/AMBER/RED scope; proven organic posts rio's paid shortlist; rio patrols spend against operator-set rules inside board's envelope; nate aims kai's funnels, queues falsifiable experiments, graduates wins their owners., **Measurement closes loop**: kai's baselines ground analysis; scorecard reconciles platform self-grades independent reads; outcomes flow back pulse's register, rio's playbooks, nate's results log, muse's concept outcomes self-annealing everywhere; instrumentation queue collects "can't measure yet.", **Cross-department**: board gates money (rio's envelopes, license spend, experiment lines); echo consumes kai's honest numbers never contradict weave's arc; vista's NSM/targets kai's grading rubric; Behavioral Science (when built) slots between lena's wording spark's gate; operator's book list (Contagious, Made Stick, Sugarman, Schwartz, StoryBrand) activates attraction half humanic strategy. · wi=**Documents first, brand.** Onboarding business filling definer templates real material: brand-identity creates kit none exists; voice guide builds real samples operator corrections; arc real history (fabricated origins honesty violations); sonic guide audio active. Until document exists, lane recommends instead blocks loudly. **All content runs pipeline.** agent ships directly; draft ends lena's humanic pass; asset ends spark's gate (GREEN engagement replies one speed-delegated zone, sweep-audited). Non-chapter content labeled ratio watched. **Volatile knowledge lives dated playbooks** (pulse's platforms, rio's platforms), reviewed cadence, refreshed kai's data operator observation never baked skills. Undated platform claims expired. **Evidence outranks patterns.** Hooks register before pattern list; paid creative proven organic; experiments judged statistics, enthusiasm; ICE/NAF flagged rubrics (rule 0.6) while ab-test-analysis stands department's one formula-verified instrument. **Money rights stay human.** Rio recommends, operator decides (auto-pause explicit capped grant); license clauses quoted, ambiguity routes counsel; spend line respects board's gate. **Weekly rhythm**: kai's scorecard (fixed shape, reds routed owners) pulse's sweeps calendar rio's patrols nate's queue spark's gate log non-chapter ratio drift notes definers. Monthly: baseline refresh contradiction audits, playbook reviews, reserve-shelf register reviews. **Rule 0.6 standing flags**: eleven logical folders placeholders. operator's priority list lena/pulse's attraction books (the system's top gap), shared statistics source (vista/sentinel/nate/kai), color science (atlas/pixel), effectiveness research (spark/rio) activates them; until rubric says it's rubric. · ds=\| Agent \| Skills \| Identity \| Operational \| Logical \| Notes \| · ds=\|---\|---\|---\|---\|---\|---\| · ds=\| spark \| 2/2 \| idea-guardian-david-ogilvy (leader) \| 5/5 \| placeholder \| coach + blocking gate \| · ds=\| atlas \| 4/4 \| — \| 5/5 \| placeholder \| brand-identity added beyond catalog \| · ds=\| lena \| 4/4 \| — \| 5/5 \| placeholder \| humanic-writing added; top book gap \| · ds=\| weave \| 2/2 \| — \| 5/5 \| placeholder \| priority build; arc + ledger \| · ds=\| tempo \| 2/2 \| — \| 5/5 \| placeholder \| audio_active switch; licensing slot converted to custom \| · ds=\| muse \| 2/2 \| — \| 5/5 \| placeholder \| 7 source refs pending \| · ds=\| pixel \| 3/3 \| — \| 5/5 \| placeholder \| generation connector = ceiling \| · ds=\| pulse \| 3/3 \| — \| 5/5 \| placeholder \| NEW agent; three-layer hooks \| · ds=\| rio \| 3/3 \| — \| 5/5 \| placeholder \| mechanics slot converted to custom \| · ds=\| nate \| 3/3 \| — \| 5/5 \| placeholder \| one Python-dependent skill \| · ds=\| kai \| 3/3 \| — \| 5/5 \| placeholder \| brand-context = the venture-skills collapse \| · ds=Department complete 2026-07-08: agents, skills (13 custom marketplace verbatim templates/registries assets), ~120 files. Pending, named: definer documents configs business (deployment work); operator's books; platform connectors (toongine bindings); Behavioral Science department (dormant review lines wait it); shared OS-level layer (web search, memory-practices).